::Primal Prime::

    He was helping move equipment onto the new base from the Ark. On his way 
back from one he fainted. He had a dream.
    In this dream all he saw were names: Megatron, Ranis, Prowl, Inferno, 
Bluestreak, Grimlock and the Dinobots. Just to name a few. He couldn't see 
their faces but he knew them from somewhere.

(Just to give you a hint think of the names, all are from this and G1. Execp 
one, that one gives you a hint as to what time period he is dreaming about.)
